<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for choosing Kingsbridge for your business insurance.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I tried to call you today to make sure you have received all of your insurance documents and to answer any questions you may have about your policy. Unfortunately, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">the contact number we have on file appears to be incorrect</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>It's important that we have the right contact details for you in case we need to get in touch about your policy. Could you </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">please reply with your preferred telephone number</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> at your earliest convenience.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Your feedback is very important to us and we would like to hear about your experience when purchasing your insurance. Our independent review service, Feefo, will be in touch via email asking you to provide feedback.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please don't hesitate to get in touch on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> if you have any queries.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
